  "body": "My mining node forked while still connected to 50 peers. I noticed it was was mining on it's own fork. I stopped ethminer but it still didn't sync. I saw a lot of TX queue full messages in the log, such as in the following snippit:\n\nhttps://gist.github.com/TalkingAntColony/b3e0837e0c422ae9ca43\n\nGeth 0.9.39/Windows on beefy PC\n\nRestarting geth found a bad block and resynced with the network in a few minutes.\n",
